        <b>PATIENT FILE: CASE #409</b>


        <color=red>STATUS:
        DECEASED</color>


        Post-mortem examination reveals severe trauma
        to the abdominal cavity.


        Upon manual palpation of the lower gastric
        region, a distinct, hard, and sharp object was clearly detected inside the
        stomach. The foreign body has caused extensive internal lacerations.


        <color=red>NOTICE:
        Proceed with immediate dissection to recover the item.

        </size>'
